      "text": "Aladdin II is an unlicensed Mega Drive port of the SNES version of Disney's Aladdin, originally made by Capcom in 1993. It might have been developed by ex-workers from Chuanpu Technology and was likely published by X Boy. This port can be considered the \"opposite\" of Aladdin 2000, a port of Virgin's Aladdin for the SNES.",
